      "content": "thanks, that makes sense. i'm worried about the stomach stuff though, i have a pretty sensitive stomach. is there a way i can do this every 2 hours without hurting my stomach? like maybe taking it with more food or something like that? i really need to get through this shift without the pain hitting me all at once.",
